I"<h4 id="plant-sonification-project">Plant Sonification Project</h4>

<p>To listen to the full song, please visit Nick Tsai‚Äôs <a href="https://soundcloud.com/nick-tsai-91907606/04-dendrobium-crumenatum/sets">Playlist</a></p>

<p><img src="http://localhost:4000/assets/img/project/plantSonification/ps1.jpeg" alt="img1" /></p>

<p>Collabrated with the electronic musician <a href="https://linktr.ee/nicktsai140">Nick Tsai</a>, Plant Sonification is an onging R&amp;D project exploring plant as a source of inspiration as well as an actual input signal for realtime music creation.</p>

<p>In addition to the plant sensor, a set of audio-triggered LED driver module was developed for the Plant Sonification Show at @mugeneration191 Cafe in Chiayi, Taiwan.</p>

